  sleep questionnaire application. The agent systematically navigated through
  the application, testing the questionnaire flow, form validation, report
  generation, and admin dashboard. Key functionalities like section navigation,
  conditional field rendering, PDF generation, and form data validation were
  confirmed to be working correctly. The agent also verified the admin login's
  authentication and error handling. During testing, minor issues were
  identified, including ESLint/TypeScript warnings in the terminal and an
  outdated page title. The agent provided a structured summary of its findings,
  highlighting both successful implementations and areas for improvement, along
  with recommendations. The user then instructed the agent to proceed with
  fixing these identified issues.
